    <!-- Question:-14
           • What is embedded style sheets?

         Answer:-

              -> Embedded Stylesheet: It allows you to define styles for a particular HTML document as a whole in one
             place. This is done by embedding the <style></style> tags containing the CSS properties in the head of your
             document.

              -> Embedded Style Sheets is a style sheet where designers can embed information of the style sheet in an
             HTML document by making use of the tags are done within head section of HTML. The syntax for embedded style
             sheets has no such exception.



